<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>HTML Demo</title>
    <style>
        /* Optional CSS styles for demonstration */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 20px;
            color: #333; /* Dark gray text */
        }
        h1 {
            color: #000; /* Black heading */
        }
        p {
            color: #666; /* Light gray paragraph text */
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 800px; /* Limit width for better readability */
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome to the HTML Demo</h1>
        <p>This page serves as a demonstration of various HTML elements.</p>
        
        <h2>HTML Elements</h2>
        <p>Below are examples of some common HTML elements:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Headings:</strong> <h1>This is a heading</h1></li>
            <li><strong>Paragraphs:</strong> <p>This is a paragraph of text.</p></li>
            <li><strong>Links:</strong> <a href="#">Link to a website</a></li>
            <li><strong>Images:</strong> <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" alt="Placeholder image"></li>
            <li><strong>List:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li>Item 1</li>
                    <li>Item 2</li>
                    <li>Item 3</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>HTML Content</h2>
        <p>Additional content for demonstration purposes:</p>
        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed ac est et diam fermentum tempus.</p>
        
        <h2>Forms</h2>
        <p>Example form:</p>
        <form action="#">
            <label for="name">Name:</label><br>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" value="John Doe"><br>
            <label for="email">Email:</label><br>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" value="john.doe@example.com"><br><br>
            <input type="submit" value="Submit">
        </form>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
